Package: mcnemarControl
Type: Package
Title: McNemar Comparisons of Multiple Treatments Against a Control
Version: 0.1.6
Authors@R: person(given = "Peter", family = "Ho", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "p.ho@leeds.ac.uk")
Description: Convenience functions to run McNemar tests comparing a control condition
    with one or more treatment conditions from long-format paired binary data, using
    the contingencytables package for asymptotic, continuity-corrected, and mid-P
    variants; and effect sizes (Cohen's g) with confidence intervals via effectsize.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
